data.description: Take a look at this clean cut brick home 5 blocks  from the beach and located in the desirable West End ''Open Sands''.  Home sits on a corner lot walking distance to the beach as neighborhood is golf cart friendly. Close proximity to all schools, Pier Park, shopping and restaurants.  Large living room adjoining the ample kitchen with plenty of cabinetry.  Ceramic tile throughout the home and no carpet.  Two full bath with one in the master bedroom.  An attached two car garage, privacy fenced throughout and sprinkler system.  At this price, this cute home will not last long.  Hot tub included but might need some work.  Short term rentals are not allowed on this street.
